He wouldn't divulge the information police had, but said the two men knew each other.

Det Insp Asnicar says police were investigating the possibility the dead man's body was moved.

He urged anyone who saw or heard anything suspicious, such as an 'unusual' looking vehicle or 'sounds of violence,' in the Edmonton area over the past two to seven days to come forward.

Hickson is due to reappear in court on December 17. 

 

